com.tailf.navu

Interface NavuCdbOperDiffIterateExtended

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NavuCdbDiffIterate, NavuCdbOperDiffIterate
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface NavuCdbOperDiffIterateExtended
extends NavuCdbOperDiffIterate
    This interface specifies additional methods for pre and post processing of a diff set iteration. Before the first diff iteration the preiterate method is called.

    For each entry in the change set one invocation per entry is done on the iterate method supplying the same instance of NavuCdbSubscriptionOperContext for the entire change set.

    The postiterate method is called after all diff set entries has been processed. NOTE: The postiterate method MUST NOT under any circumstances hang subsequent execution of the subscriber thread which could lead to the whole NCS could hang indefinitely.
